result.name: Yaadgar Kebabs And Curries

reviews.text: Good place to have Indian cursine as a quick lunch in Sai Kung. The chicken curry tastes very nicely.

Ordered this food with Food panda. It took more than 1.5hours to be delivered! Food panda contacted me to notify me that the food was not ready for the delivery person. By the time it arrive it was far later than what we had planned for.
Nice Indian fast food
Very good in Indian style food.
Best Kebab in Sai Kung. Decent price. Friendly staff. Try their garlic naan bread as an appetizer - really good.
